          "CORRECTION": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "F is the total correction factor of the activity,",
                "F=fs*fc*fg. fs, fc and fg are correction factors for",
                "the self-absorption of the sample at a given gamma-ray",
                "energy, the coincidence sum effect of cascade",
                "gamma-rays of the investigated nuclide and the",
                "counting geometry, respectively.",
                "Correction factors for the self-absorption:",
                "******************************************************",
                "                           Samples thickness h (cm)",
                "Gamma-ray energy (keV)********************************",
